---
description: 
globs: **/*.liquid,**/*.js,**/*.css
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use sections and blocks to create reusable components
- Optimize images and assets for faster loading times
- Implement responsive design using CSS Grid and Flexbox
- Utilize Shopify's built-in features like AJAX for dynamic content loading
- Follow Liquid best practices for performance and maintainability

- Use color schemes functionality instead of adding color settings to each feature.
- All theme specific javascript files should load with 'defer' attribute, never create parse blocking javascript includes.

